<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>71</hymn_number>
<key>Eb</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 A sual cia vawlei cung mi kha, Pathian nih a dawt hna; A tha bik
 khamhnak sung bik kha, Man loin a pek hna.

[C1]
   Maw khuaruahharnak ngaingai, Jesuh a kan dawt nak; Kannih khamhnak
   ca Amah cu Kalvari ah a thi.

[V2]
 Kan zumh ahcun kan Bawi a si, A nung than Pathian Fa, Thihnak in a kan
 khamh cang i, A thi in a kan tawl,

[C2]
   Maw khuaruahharnak ngaingai, Jesuh a kan dawt nak; Kannih khamhnak
   ca Amah cu Kalvari ah a thi.

[V3]
 Dawtnak in a tlinter dih cang, A mithiang hna sinah, Bawi Jesuh bia an
 zumh caah, Dinhdaihnak kha an hmuh,

[C3]
   Maw khuaruahharnak ngaingai, Jesuh a kan dawt nak; Kannih khamhnak
   ca Amah cu Kalvari ah a thi.

[V4]
 A zummi lunglawm in kal u, Vancung a tha inn ah, Vawlei ah nan zumhnak
 bangin, Vancung ah nan hmuh lai.

[C4]
   Maw khuaruahharnak ngaingai, Jesuh a kan dawt nak; Kannih khamhnak
   ca Amah cu Kalvari ah a thi.</lyrics>
<title>KHUARUAHHAR DAWTNAK CH71</title>
</song>